---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Jakob Højgaard">
  <div class="animate-fade-in py-20 max-w-[640px]">
    <p class="font-body text-sm text-accent tracking-[2px] uppercase mb-5 font-medium">About</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-[48px] font-semibold text-text-primary leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-8">
      Jakob Højgaard
    </h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        I'm a Danish technologist living on the Sunshine Coast in Queensland, Australia.
        I currently serve as Group Executive and Chief Information Officer at Loan Market Group,
        Australia's largest mortgage broker aggregation company, where I lead teams across
        web development, security, and cross-platform mobile development.
      </p>

      <p>
        With over 17 years of experience as a director, full-stack engineer, and architect,
        I've spent most of my career at the intersection of enterprise technology and financial services.
        I'm particularly interested in how modern engineering practices can transform industries
        that have been slow to adopt them.
      </p>

      <p>
        I'm also building <strong>Fundhaus</strong>, a fintech platform focused on mortgage refinancing
        that matches borrowers with lenders — applying everything I've learned about the mortgage
        industry from the technology side.
      </p>

      <p>
        Outside of work, I'm a brewer, a rookie surfer, and a father of three. I write here about
        the things I'm learning and thinking about — technology, startups, leadership, and occasionally
        the things that don't fit neatly into any category.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <h3>Get in touch</h3>
      <p>
        The best way to reach me is on <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourprofile">LinkedIn</a>.
        I'm also on <a href="https://github.com/yourprofile">GitHub</a> and <a href="https://x.com/yourprofile">X</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
